{"id": 1957, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些时候，你觉得“量化思维”被滥用了？", "description": "数据是挺重要的，但是，真的有必要那么无孔不入吗？以及，真的靠谱吗？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 8513, "comment_count": 23, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171015164347pZfxIBamX2bLezT9.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-16T17:00:12Z", "questions": [{"id": 3134, "title": "哪些时候，你觉得“量化思维”被滥用了？", "content": "哪些时候，你觉得量化思维被滥用了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 241929, "content": "“大数据”扮演一个噱头，没人关心样本和方法以及结论到底对不对", "image": "img/option/option/20171015174431MLUaFj3Kk80Dn7Wb.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 241930, "content": "用数字衡量一切成就，职业规划很多围绕“毕业三年收入翻倍”", "image": "img/option/option/2017101517580928oK7I3ndEaPfFmJ.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 241931, "content": "用算法筛选各种事物，从听歌到阅读的信息，都由“猜你喜欢”决定", "image": "img/option/option/20171016142621BACi7aEKF50znXpP.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242005, "content": "认为只有数据才是可靠的，比如工作总结一定要罗列大量数据", "image": "img/option/option/20171016142916yUGliCY9gHOrqxbk.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242027, "content": "数字上的急功近利，市场上充斥“一百天掌握英文写作”之类的畅销书", "image": "img/option/option/20171016143041iCQ493UqajevTGEX.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242028, "content": "“排行榜”化思维，买东西都是“畅销榜”“人气榜”放在醒目位置", "image": "img/option/option/20171016143303uhrmzAcGaJ7T39Q2.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242029, "content": "“破纪录”化思维，电影票房、双十一销量……达到一个新的数值后就陷入狂欢", "image": "img/option/option/20171016143539sU7rHayCn6zVdT2I.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242030, "content": "“测评贴量化”思维，“我们测试了一百个XXX”即靠谱的保证", "image": "img/option/option/20171016144109iTWl1aAZKmCyhukU.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}